amendatorysection.catchline:
Administrator of facility operated
primarily for caring for persons with head injuries and associated disorders;
license required; qualifications; renewal.

amendatorysection.para:
(A)
A psychologist pursuant to the Uniform Credentialing Act, with at least a
master's degree in psychology from an accredited college or university;

(B) A physician
licensed pursuant to the Uniform Credentialing Act to practice medicine and
surgery or psychiatry;

(D) A certified social worker, a certified
master social worker, or a licensed mental health practitioner pursuant to
the Uniform Credentialing Act;
